{"tid":2127803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生防護中心：【當街除罩食煙  隨時罰款二千】","createTime":"2020-07-27T13:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:30:24.000Z","uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"43cbf006c838175076b6c7430491c8dce96eec7e","tid":2127803,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"【當街除罩食煙  隨時罰款二千】<br />\n<br />\n本周三(7月29日)起，根據《預防及控制疾病(佩戴口罩)規例》(第599I章)，任何人在室內或室外公眾地方均須戴上口罩，違者可處定額罰款$2,000。<br />\n<br />\n除罩食煙摸口摸鼻，病毒隨時乘虛而入。為己為人，今日起戒煙。<br />\n<br />\n打1833 183免費戒煙。經評估後合適的人士可獲郵遞免費藥物，助你足不出戶輕鬆戒煙。<br />\n<br />\n戒煙專題網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.livetobaccofree.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.livetobaccofree.hk&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=536a82b8\" target=\"_blank\">www.livetobaccofree.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n戒煙應用程式<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.livetobaccofree.hk/tc/free-quit-tools/download-quit-app.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livetobaccofree.hk%2Ftc%2Ffree-quit-tools%2Fdownload-quit-app.html&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3df5a62d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livetobaccofree.hk/tc/free-quit-tools/download-quit-app.html</a><br />\n<br />\n更多防疫資訊，請瀏覽2019冠狀病毒病專題網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=021998fb\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #COVID19 #2019冠狀病毒病 #戒煙 #立即戒煙 #QuitNow #QuitSmokingNow<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPGnpa2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPGnpa2.jpg&h=588c4d49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adc13c38ddfdd89d4a567997d3a7e43fec496dee","tid":2127803,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"廢佬：驚條撚 肺癌都唔驚 我驚肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"